{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/study/date_time/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hong_devlog","author":"hongdev","siteUrl":"https://hong-dev.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"hong-dev/hong-dev.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"33db2a57-9112-5d95-ba66-a73204ab5bad","excerpt":"new Date() 현재 날짜와 시간까지 나온다. 시간이 흐른다고 해서 이 값이 변하지는 않는다. 코드가 실행되는 순간의 현재 시간이 담긴다. 특정 날짜를 parameter로 넘겨주면, 해당 날짜의 Date를 반환할 수 있다. GMT (Greenwich Mean Time) 컴퓨터 언어에서는 GMT 기준으로 시간을 알려준다. 한국표준시는 GMT+0900으로 표시된다. new Date()에서 원하는 정보 뽑아내기 new Date()가 반환된 값을 그대로 사용하지 않는다. new Date…","html":"<h2 id=\"new-date\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-date\" aria-label=\"new date permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>new Date()</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>현재 날짜와 시간까지 나온다.</li>\n<li>시간이 흐른다고 해서 이 값이 변하지는 않는다. 코드가 실행되는 순간의 현재 시간이 담긴다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> rightNow <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"특정-날짜를-parameter로-넘겨주면-해당-날짜의-date를-반환할-수-있다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A0%95-%EB%82%A0%EC%A7%9C%EB%A5%BC-parameter%EB%A1%9C-%EB%84%98%EA%B2%A8%EC%A3%BC%EB%A9%B4-%ED%95%B4%EB%8B%B9-%EB%82%A0%EC%A7%9C%EC%9D%98-date%EB%A5%BC-%EB%B0%98%ED%99%98%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"특정 날짜를 parameter로 넘겨주면 해당 날짜의 date를 반환할 수 있다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특정 날짜를 parameter로 넘겨주면, 해당 날짜의 Date를 반환할 수 있다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> date1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'December 17, 2019 03:24:00'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> date2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2019-12-17T03:24:00'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> date3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2019</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"gmt-greenwich-mean-time\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gmt-greenwich-mean-time\" aria-label=\"gmt greenwich mean time permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>GMT (Greenwich Mean Time)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>컴퓨터 언어에서는 GMT 기준으로 시간을 알려준다.</li>\n<li>한국표준시는 GMT+0900으로 표시된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"new-date에서-원하는-정보-뽑아내기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-date%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%9B%90%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4-%EB%BD%91%EC%95%84%EB%82%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"new date에서 원하는 정보 뽑아내기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>new Date()에서 원하는 정보 뽑아내기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>new Date()가 반환된 값을 그대로 사용하지 않는다.<br>\nnew Date() 값에서 Date 타입이 가지고 있는 method를 활용하여 값을 받아온다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> rightNow <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//2020-02-09T11:58:06.187Z</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> year <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getFullYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">//2020</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> month <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getMonth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">//2</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> date <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>           <span class=\"token comment\">//9</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> day <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getDay</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">//0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> currentHour <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getHours</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">//20</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> currentMin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getMinutes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//58</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">getMonth</code> 함수는, 현재 달보다 1 작은 값이 반환되므로 주의한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"gettime\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gettime\" aria-label=\"gettime permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>getTime</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>날짜의 밀리초 표현을 반환한다.</li>\n<li>기준이 되는 일자는 1970년 1월 1일로, 이 날짜로부터 getTime의 밀리초만큼 지났다는 의미다.</li>\n<li>getTime 함수로 비교연산을 통해 언제가 더 과거인지 판단할 수 있다.<br>\n값이 작으면 과거이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> rightNow <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> time <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rightNow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//1581250598788</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] 날짜와 시간","date":"January 30, 2020","category":"javascript","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/study/date_time/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/study/math/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] Math method","category":"javascript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/study/data_type/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] Data Type","category":"javascript","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2353110810","3128451518"]}